<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 10:07:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列袭击伊朗，据报道无人机袭击了伊斯法罕附近的军事目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article-live/reports-say-israel-attacked-site-in-iran-explosions-heard-in-isfahan/0000018e-f484-daad-a3de-febf4f4e0000</link><description>以色列官员向《华盛顿邮报》证实对伊朗进行空袭 ■ 据《纽约时报》报道，三名伊朗官员称袭击袭击了伊朗西部伊斯法罕附近的军事基地 ■ 美国对伊朗无人机计划、钢铁、汽车工业实施新制裁 ■ 美国否决巴勒斯坦加入联合国的请求■ 标准普尔下调以色列信用评级</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 04:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article-live/reports-say-israel-attacked-site-in-iran-explosions-heard-in-isfahan/0000018e-f484-daad-a3de-febf4f4e0000</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》报道伊朗空军基地在以色列袭击中遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-19/ty-article/israeli-missiles-hit-a-site-in-iran-abc-news-reports-iran-suspends-flights-above-cities/0000018e-f42c-daad-a3de-fe3f48450000</link><description>伊朗电视台称，在宣布防空系统已启动后，核设施在报道中的袭击中未受损</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 03:15:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-19/ty-article/israeli-missiles-hit-a-site-in-iran-abc-news-reports-iran-suspends-flights-above-cities/0000018e-f42c-daad-a3de-fe3f48450000</guid></item><item><title>数百人在威尼斯双年展以色列馆外抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-protest-outside-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-f3b2-df38-abbf-ffbab06f0000</link><description>在这场著名的艺术活动中，亲巴勒斯坦抗议者指责以色列实施种族灭绝，而活动人士则在城市各处悬挂了 40 件巴勒斯坦艺术家的作品</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 00:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-protest-outside-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-f3b2-df38-abbf-ffbab06f0000</guid></item><item><title>标准普尔下调以色列信用评级，理由是与伊朗的军事升级风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-19/ty-article/s-p-says-israels-long-term-credit-outlook-negative-iran-tensions-increasing-risk/0000018e-f38b-d240-a19f-f78b9f0b0000</link><description>负面前景反映了以色列与哈马斯战争以及与真主党或伊朗的对抗可能对以色列经济的影响超过该机构目前预期的风险</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-19/ty-article/s-p-says-israels-long-term-credit-outlook-negative-iran-tensions-increasing-risk/0000018e-f38b-d240-a19f-f78b9f0b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列招标建造拥有 1,000 多套住房的东耶路撒冷新犹太社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-bids-new-jewish-neighborhood-in-east-jerusalem-with-over-1-000-housing-units/0000018e-f2bf-d87e-a58e-f7bf7adf0000</link><description>以色列土地管理局周三发出了该社区建设投标邀请，距地区规划界批准仅三个月——与其他类似项目相比，时间非常短</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:27:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-bids-new-jewish-neighborhood-in-east-jerusalem-with-over-1-000-housing-units/0000018e-f2bf-d87e-a58e-f7bf7adf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯战争如何将这个安静的犹太郊区变成战区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-israel-hamas-war-turned-this-quiet-jewish-suburb-into-a-battle-zone/0000018e-ebda-d7e3-a9bf-ffffa62a0000</link><description>纽约郊区提内克是犹太人聚集的地方，已成为加沙战争导致犹太穆斯林紧张关系的导火索。一位相关的当地拉比表示，“有一种感觉，这超出了通常的反以色列活动”，而另一位拉比则称该镇的抗议活动是“公然的恐吓”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-israel-hamas-war-turned-this-quiet-jewish-suburb-into-a-battle-zone/0000018e-ebda-d7e3-a9bf-ffffa62a0000</guid></item><item><title>“一位澳大利亚朋友告诉我：如果发生核战争，就来这里重建家园”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/an-aussie-friend-told-me-if-theres-nuclear-war-come-here-and-rebuild-yourselves/0000018e-f2b6-d240-a19f-f6b7da3b0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名澳大利亚移民在战争期间拒绝离开以色列，因为“这就是这里的生活”，一名军官在六个月的预备役后重新适应文明社会</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:08:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/an-aussie-friend-told-me-if-theres-nuclear-war-come-here-and-rebuild-yourselves/0000018e-f2b6-d240-a19f-f6b7da3b0000</guid></item><item><title>被伊朗导弹击伤的 7 岁贝都因女孩的家人为她祈祷，并为她提供庇护所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/family-of-7-year-old-bedouin-girl-wounded-by-iranian-missile-pray-for-her-and-shelters/0000018e-f24b-d620-abaf-f26b20120000</link><description>女孩受伤后的几天里，只有一名内阁部长探望过她的家人。尽管她因村庄没有避难所而受伤，正在为生命而战，但以色列国防军和政府仍在吹嘘军队防空系统的成功</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/family-of-7-year-old-bedouin-girl-wounded-by-iranian-missile-pray-for-her-and-shelters/0000018e-f24b-d620-abaf-f26b20120000</guid></item><item><title>事实上，威尼斯双年展上有一个以色列展览</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/actually-there-is-an-israeli-exhibit-at-the-venice-biennale/0000018e-f153-ddac-a59e-f9db55e90000</link><description>露丝·帕蒂尔（Ruth Patir）关于在加沙没有停火且人质被扣押的情况下不开放以色列馆的标语本身已成为一种装置。另外，来自贝埃里基布兹的独特客座项目以及为什么以色列人在这个可怕的时代阅读更多恐怖小说</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/actually-there-is-an-israeli-exhibit-at-the-venice-biennale/0000018e-f153-ddac-a59e-f9db55e90000</guid></item><item><title>“我被教导种族灭绝永远不应该再次发生”：吉尔斯坦诉以色列国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-was-taught-genocide-should-never-happen-again-jill-stein-vs-the-state-of-israel/0000018e-f28f-dea6-ab9e-f28f095d0000</link><description>在2016年美国总统选举中，吉尔·斯坦作为绿党候选人获得了150万张选票，削弱了希拉里·克林顿的实力，甚至可能帮助唐纳德·特朗普赢得了胜利。今天，她的民调支持率为 4%，她可能会再次成为剧透。但现在，10 月 7 日之后，哈佛犹太医生的战斗口号是对抗以色列</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:35:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-was-taught-genocide-should-never-happen-again-jill-stein-vs-the-state-of-israel/0000018e-f28f-dea6-ab9e-f28f095d0000</guid></item><item><title>谷歌因抗议公司与以色列的交易而解雇了 28 名员工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/google-fires-28-employees-after-protesting-against-companys-deal-with-israel/0000018e-f204-daad-a3de-fe3ff3740000</link><description>抗议活动是由一个名为“No Tech for Apartheid”的组织组织的，该组织的成员在现场告诉记者，他们反对 Nimbus 项目——谷歌和亚马逊于 2021 年获得价值 12 亿美元的合同，为以色列政府提供云计算服务</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/google-fires-28-employees-after-protesting-against-companys-deal-with-israel/0000018e-f204-daad-a3de-fe3ff3740000</guid></item><item><title>为什么一段加沙人在海滩上疯传的视频让以色列人抓狂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-18/ty-article/.highlight/why-a-viral-video-of-gazans-at-the-beach-is-driving-israelis-mad/0000018e-f213-d620-abaf-f273f7fc0000</link><description>一张图片可能抵得上一千个字，但在当今社交媒体和 24 小时新闻循环、真相被叙述所取代的时代，这一千个字有很多——太多了——版本</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-18/ty-article/.highlight/why-a-viral-video-of-gazans-at-the-beach-is-driving-israelis-mad/0000018e-f213-d620-abaf-f273f7fc0000</guid></item><item><title>从加沙到伊朗，内塔尼亚胡政府正在危及以色列的生存</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/from-gaza-to-iran-the-netanyahu-government-is-endangering-israels-survival/0000018e-f25f-daad-a3de-fe7ff5790000</link><description>以色列正面临历史性失败，这是多年来灾难性政策的苦果。如果该国现在将复仇置于其自身最大利益之上，它将把自己和整个地区置于严重危险之中</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/from-gaza-to-iran-the-netanyahu-government-is-endangering-israels-survival/0000018e-f25f-daad-a3de-fe7ff5790000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡真的认为以色列可以单独对抗伊朗吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/does-netanyahu-really-think-israel-can-take-on-iran-alone/0000018e-f1cf-daad-a3de-fffff8460000</link><description>以色列的军事和技术实力在非凡的国际联盟的支持下击退了该地区周日仍发誓要摧毁以色列的原教旨主义势力。但很快这种战略综合可能就会成为过去</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/does-netanyahu-really-think-israel-can-take-on-iran-alone/0000018e-f1cf-daad-a3de-fffff8460000</guid></item><item><title>他们紧密结合的基布兹被哈马斯摧毁了。现在他们正在寻求不同的前进道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-close-knit-kibbutz-was-destroyed-by-hamas-now-they-seek-separate-ways-forward/0000018e-ed4a-d240-a19f-fd4b9f410000</link><description>贝埃里社区在大屠杀当天失去了近 100 名成员，目前仍分散在全国各地。现在每个家庭都需要对其未来做出决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:01:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-close-knit-kibbutz-was-destroyed-by-hamas-now-they-seek-separate-ways-forward/0000018e-ed4a-d240-a19f-fd4b9f410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院讨论了加沙的饥饿问题。只是缺少紧迫感</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-supreme-court-discussed-the-starving-of-gaza-only-the-urgency-was-missing/0000018e-e74d-d95b-afbe-ff4db7c70000</link><description>法官们并没有猛烈抨击政府，他们选择了温和的激进主义，尽管据信加沙北部大约三分之一的儿童患有严重营养不良</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 17:20:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-supreme-court-discussed-the-starving-of-gaza-only-the-urgency-was-missing/0000018e-e74d-d95b-afbe-ff4db7c70000</guid></item><item><title>住房、淋浴、电力：这些是以色列军队在加沙市中心建造的前哨基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/housing-showers-electricity-these-are-the-outposts-the-idf-is-building-in-central-gaza/0000018e-f1da-dbb3-a3bf-f5df02120000</link><description>卫星图像和地面镜头显示了分隔加沙地带的关键走廊的前线哨所，其中包括看起来像是将返回加沙北部的巴勒斯坦人检查设施</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 17:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/housing-showers-electricity-these-are-the-outposts-the-idf-is-building-in-central-gaza/0000018e-f1da-dbb3-a3bf-f5df02120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 195 天：哈马斯官员称该组织尚未放弃停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-195-hamas-official-says-group-hasnt-abandoned-truce-talks/0000018e-f21e-d240-a19f-f61fb9380001</link><description>伊朗高级指挥官：在以色列威胁报复的情况下，德黑兰可能会审查其“核学说” 美国高级官员告诉美国广播公司新闻，以色列在逾越节之前不太可能对伊朗进行报复 美国和以色列官员举行虚拟会议，讨论以色列在叙利亚开展地面行动的计划拉法 ■ 哈马斯高级官员表示，该组织尚未放弃停火谈判 ■ 卡塔尔“重新评估”作为调解人的角色 ■ 战争结束 195 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-195-hamas-official-says-group-hasnt-abandoned-truce-talks/0000018e-f21e-d240-a19f-f61fb9380001</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方以涉嫌煽动恐怖罪逮捕巴勒斯坦学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/police-probe-palestinian-scholar-doubting-oct-7-sexual-violence-on-suspicion-of-incitement/0000018e-f1a4-daad-a3de-ffbf42e40000</link><description>Nadera Shalhoub-Kevorkian 教授被带到耶路撒冷附近的警察局接受调查。她的律师表示，这是一次非法逮捕，其目的是恐吓以色列学院中的任何批评声音。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:20:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/police-probe-palestinian-scholar-doubting-oct-7-sexual-violence-on-suspicion-of-incitement/0000018e-f1a4-daad-a3de-ffbf42e40000</guid></item><item><title>15名证人，三份供词，裸体尸体模型。 10月7日哈马斯强奸的所有证据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/witnesses-confessions-naked-dead-bodies-all-the-evidence-of-hamas-rape-on-oct-7/0000018e-f114-d92e-abfe-f77f7e3f0000</link><description>哈马斯 10 月 7 日的强奸行为已成为大屠杀中最具争议的话题之一。每一个出现的证词和细节都在以色列支持者和反对者之间的冲突中被武器化。现在，根据与数十位消息人士的对话，《国土报》的一项调查勾画出了哈马斯实施性犯罪的证据，以及缺失的证据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:12:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/witnesses-confessions-naked-dead-bodies-all-the-evidence-of-hamas-rape-on-oct-7/0000018e-f114-d92e-abfe-f77f7e3f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>